{"tid":1564242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大大聲跟我講一次，《願榮光歸香港》就係香港國歌","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T22:39:50.000Z","uid":63095,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d56f5eb23c613708e959978ecc3e26405e945764","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"你當首歌係抗爭進行曲，就係晚晚搞緊嘉年華！<br />\n<br />\n你當首歌係香港國歌，就係搞緊港獨，邊樣對政權有威脅啲啊，唔洗我講都知啦！"},{"pid":"2468c0a0c7f0b7261258cf959930d2da629c29ff","tid":1564242,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9930d75cf44cf984fb490512fe5779214440b7a1","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"何以　這土地　淚再流<br />\n何以　令眾人　亦憤恨<br />\n昂首　拒默沉　吶喊聲　響透<br />\n盼自由　歸於　這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以　這恐懼　抹不走<br />\n何以　為信念　從沒退後<br />\n何解　血在流　但邁進聲　響透<br />\n建自由　光輝　香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星　墜落　徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡　最遠處吹來　號角聲<br />\n捍自由　來齊集這裡　來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣　智慧　也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到　要光復　這香港<br />\n同行兒女　為正義　時代革命<br />\n祈求　民主與自由　萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"0574f4ce9fcfab4ee7beba45a7ee0d1b5476e910","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"何以　這土地　淚再流"},{"pid":"ec8e0c41cb1e3e92b2f42e4fd6999375da28be12","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"何以　令眾人　亦憤恨"},{"pid":"217b1362bacc6f069bcc953cec1227287c1c2fe0","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"昂首　拒默沉　吶喊聲　響透"},{"pid":"d1e085686d8786ab078ec455146a85d6281c495c","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"盼自由　歸於　這裡"},{"pid":"53639bd4b2e8219f1994d682ee814d14bef7f8e5","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"何以　這恐懼　抹不走"},{"pid":"35fc0f9d70a8d1e57eb5cc597768f88ccea20cc8","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"何以　為信念　從沒退後"},{"pid":"5ed2793ed00a63098444453e53b19f993b47b54f","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"何解　血在流　但邁進聲　響透"},{"pid":"63fa549f1757f89bd866bfe8f8998cc4d68ffe62","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"建自由　光輝　香港"},{"pid":"e22f75f13f8b927433052767bc1929fa8bc0583c","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"在晚星　墜落　徬徨午夜"},{"pid":"bec52814bbb6c97dbd7f8619b6070866693baedf","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"迷霧裡　最遠處吹來　號角聲"},{"pid":"69630f7fc1282aaf616efcb3de57fc708428ee4a","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"捍自由　來齊集這裡　來全力抗對"},{"pid":"e246d14178d34ee3cd494688ae2ece673e8828f3","tid":1564242,"uid":63095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"勇氣　